sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant DFS as DFS task<br/>(rayon worker for start v)
    participant Gate as Fullness gate<br/>(n_full ≥ γ·n)
    participant GMin as AtomicU64<br/>global_min
    participant Heap as per_vertex heap[c]<br/>(c ∈ cycle)
    participant NFull as AtomicUsize<br/>n_full_heaps

    Note over DFS,NFull: Initialisation
    DFS->>GMin: load = +Inf
    DFS->>NFull: load = 0

    Note over DFS,Heap: Recursive DFS step
    DFS->>Gate: nfull = load(NFull)
    Gate-->>DFS: gate_satisfied = (nfull ≥ ⌈γ·n⌉)
    alt gate open AND any_full
        DFS->>GMin: load → threshold
        DFS->>DFS: ub = scorer.upper_bound(...)
        alt ub ≤ threshold
            Note right of DFS: PRUNE branch
        else
            DFS->>DFS: recurse into nxt
        end
    else
        Note right of DFS: ABB off → recurse unconditionally
    end

    Note over DFS,Heap: Closed cycle emit
    DFS->>Heap: push(score=s, cycle)
    alt heap newly full
        Heap->>NFull: fetch_add(1)
        Heap->>GMin: atomic_min(peek().score)
    else heap min decreased
        Heap->>GMin: atomic_min(peek().score)
    end
